01915 /* Allocates the stack if it does not exist.
01916  *  Guarantees space for at least one push.
01917  */
01918 static void ganesha_yyensure_buffer_stack (void)
01919 {
01920         int num_to_alloc;
01921     
01922         if (!(yy_buffer_stack)) {
01923 
01924                 /* First allocation is just for 2 elements, since we don't know if this
01925                  * scanner will even need a stack. We use 2 instead of 1 to avoid an
01926                  * immediate realloc on the next call.
01927          */
01928                 num_to_alloc = 1;
01929                 (yy_buffer_stack) = (struct yy_buffer_state**)ganesha_yyalloc
01930                                                                 (num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*)
01931                                                                 );
01932                 if ( ! (yy_buffer_stack) )
01933                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "out of dynamic memory in ganesha_yyensure_buffer_stack()" );
01934                                                                   
01935                 memset((yy_buffer_stack), 0, num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*));
01936                                 
01937                 (yy_buffer_stack_max) = num_to_alloc;
01938                 (yy_buffer_stack_top) = 0;
01939                 return;
01940         }
01941 
01942         if ((yy_buffer_stack_top) >= ((yy_buffer_stack_max)) - 1){
01943 
01944                 /* Increase the buffer to prepare for a possible push. */
01945                 int grow_size = 8 /* arbitrary grow size */;
01946 
01947                 num_to_alloc = (yy_buffer_stack_max) + grow_size;
01948                 (yy_buffer_stack) = (struct yy_buffer_state**)ganesha_yyrealloc
01949                                                                 ((yy_buffer_stack),
01950                                                                 num_to_alloc * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*)
01951                                                                 );
01952                 if ( ! (yy_buffer_stack) )
01953                         YY_FATAL_ERROR( "out of dynamic memory in ganesha_yyensure_buffer_stack()" );
01954 
01955                 /* zero only the new slots.*/
01956                 memset((yy_buffer_stack) + (yy_buffer_stack_max), 0, grow_size * sizeof(struct yy_buffer_state*));
01957                 (yy_buffer_stack_max) = num_to_alloc;
01958         }
